\mt1 Hosea
\is1 Introduction
\ip The seini baseen meyitenged te intagne dengan ni prupita Husiyas anak ni Biiri te me walu gatus (800) leg‑un te ware pad neetew si Jesus. Nekeg-iling si prupita Husiyas and si Amus migpanagne diye te me etew te iling ded timpu. Piru migpabulus-bulus mule migpanagne si Husiyas te nenakasinundul pad me leg‑un. Te seeye timpu, nabaad te daruwa ka inged te Israil and diye migwali si Husiyas te ampew baad senge-kakuwa egngaranan din te Israil, and senge-kakuwa egngaranan man‑e te Ipraim. Ipraim ka ngaran te amana impurtanti tribu diye te ampew baad. Ne ka Samarya ka iney siyudad. Ne ka deisek baad te inged te Israil, ingngaranan din te Huda. Migwali sikandin te ware pad dereeti ka Samarya te miglusud me kuntere dan.
\ip Te seini baseen, impapitew ni Husiyas ka pegsupak te keet-etawan te Magbebaye Manama and ka peg-engked dan kandin. Egpekeiling sikandan te masinupaken asawa rin si Gumir and mig-engked kandin. Ne amana nalaggew si Husiyas tenged te pegsupak te me etew and migsimba te me diyus-diyus, and warad e migsalig te Magbebaye Manama. Piru te katammanan, iyan ded iya egdapit ka geyinawa te Manama te keet-etawan din and egpakalibed ded man‑e sikandan diye te kandin. Dakel amana ka geyinawa rin kandan, and impanengneng din seini kayi te amana makalulunu me lalag, “Egmenuwen ku sikeykew te eg-engked, he Ipraim? Kene ku iya sikeykew egbalaharen egkatalu, he Israil. Kene ku sikeykew egdereetan iling te Adma and Sibuwim. Kene egpakatuhut ka pusung ku te iling due, su dakel ka geyinawa ku keykew.” (11:8).
